query:
SELECT c.id, c.name, fl.id as floorLevelId, fl.levelName, fl.mapImageUrl 
FROM shopping_centres c 
LEFT JOIN floor_levels fl ON fl.centreId = c.id 
WHERE c.name LIKE '%Chullora%';
